OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781482667
OL,3,CQatari officials arrive in Tehran to
OL,4,Chelp finalise US-Iran peace deal
OL,6,FQatari mediators have arrived in
OL,7,FTehran to finalise an agreement with
OL,8,Fthe US after Donald Trump said the
OL,9,Fdeal was imminent.
OL,11,FTrump and Pakistani Prime Minister
OL,12,FShehbaz Sharif said on Saturday that
OL,13,Fthe deal would be signed on Sunday.
OL,14,FIran was more cautious about the idea,
OL,15,Fwith spokesperson Esmail Baghaei
OL,16,Fsaying it could happen in the coming
OL,17,Fdays.
OL,19,FTrump said that the Strait of Hormuz
OL,20,Fwould open immediately after the
OL,21,Fsigning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781482667
OL,3,CQatari officials arrive in Tehran to
OL,4,Chelp finalise US-Iran peace deal
OL,6,FThe deal is expected to be signed
OL,7,Felectronically, without an in-person
OL,8,Fceremony, though it's unclear when or
OL,9,Fhow the signing will take place.
OL,11,FThe deal does not solve the thorniest
OL,12,Fissues between the US and Iran,
OL,13,Fincluding Iran's nuclear program or
OL,14,Fits frozen assets.
OL,16,FInstead, it offers a 60-day framework
OL,17,Ffor technical discussions on those
OL,18,Fissues, Pakistani officials told the
OL,19,FAssociated Press.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781482667
OL,3,CQatari officials arrive in Tehran to
OL,4,Chelp finalise US-Iran peace deal
OL,6,FPakistan has operated as a key
OL,7,Fmediator during the war, often keeping
OL,8,Fboth sides together when they appeared
OL,9,Fready to walk out of negotiations
OL,10,Fcompletely.
OL,12,FUnder the current deal being
OL,13,Fdiscussed, US and Israel appear to
OL,14,Fhave fallen short of their original
OL,15,Fgoals of destroying Iran's missile and
OL,16,Fnuclear programs and ending its
OL,17,Fsupport for proxies.
OL,19,FIt is not clear how the deal will
OL,20,Faddress these issues, or if they will
OL,21,Fbe part of the final agreement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
