PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781482667
OL,3,CQatari officials arrive in Tehran to
OL,4,Chelp finalise US-Iran peace deal
OL,6,FTrump on social media asserted that
OL,7,F"when all is calm," the US would go in
OL,8,Fand "downblend and destroy" the
OL,9,Fenriched uranium in Iran or in the US.
OL,11,FIran has 440.9kg of uranium that is
OL,12,Fenriched up to 60% purity, a short,
OL,13,Ftechnical step from weapons-grade
OL,14,Flevels of 90%, according to the
OL,15,FInternational Atomic Energy Agency.
