CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781482667
OL,3,CQatari officials arrive in Tehran to
OL,4,Chelp finalise US-Iran peace deal
OL,6,FOn Saturday, a US official said there
OL,7,Fare five key terms in the agreement:
OL,8,FIran's nuclear material will be
OL,9,Fdestroyed and removed, its nuclear
OL,10,Fprogram will be dismantled, none of
OL,11,Fits frozen money will be released
OL,12,Funtil it meets certain demands, the
OL,13,FStrait of Hormuz will be open, and
OL,14,FIran must not fund terrorist groups.
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
