FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1781482667
OL,3,CQatari officials arrive in Tehran to
OL,4,Chelp finalise US-Iran peace deal
OL,6,FThe deal in its current form is a deep
OL,7,Fdisappointment to Israel's government,
OL,8,Fwhich has been sidelined in
OL,9,Fnegotiations led by Pakistan and
OL,10,Fothers.
OL,12,FEven critics in Trump's own Republican
OL,13,FParty, struggling with an unpopular
OL,14,Fwar ahead of the midterm elections,
OL,15,Fcriticised the deal. Some said it did
OL,16,Fnot improve on the terms of the 2015
OL,17,FIran nuclear deal that Trump withdrew
OL,18,Fthe US from during his first term and
OL,19,Fwhich he still describes as "bad."
